dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, islands off coast, boundaries, places of historical interest.
Features decorative cartouche and a pictorial vignette of cherubs.
Appears in Le grand atlas, ou, Cosmographie Blaviane ... À Amsterdam : Chez Jean Blaeu, 1663.
